{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer-service", "channel": "customer-feedback", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "Hi team, just a reminder that our customer satisfaction survey is going live next Monday. Please make sure to share the link with your customers and encourage them to provide feedback.", "create_at": 1690345200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "jlee", "message": "I've scheduled a meeting with the marketing team to discuss our grand opening promotions strategy. If anyone would like to join, please let me know and I'll send over the invite.", "create_at": 1690350800000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer-service", "channel": "customer-feedback", "user": "skim", "message": "Hi David, I had a customer complaint about our return policy. They felt it was unclear and caused some confusion. Should we revisit our policy and make some adjustments?", "create_at": 1690354400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "jlee", "message": "Just a heads up that the IT team will be conducting some system maintenance this weekend, which may cause some disruptions to our inventory management system.", "create_at": 1690358000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer-service", "channel": "customer-feedback", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "Great point Sophia, I think it's time we review our return policy and make some changes. Can you work on drafting an updated version and I'll review it?", "create_at": 1690361600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "jlee", "message": "Also, don't forget that our quarterly team meeting is scheduled for next Thursday at 2 PM. We'll be discussing our progress and goals for the next quarter.", "create_at": 1690365200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "jlee", "message": "Hello team, I'd like to share our Q3 2024 new store openings report. We've successfully opened 12 new locations across the US, with 4 in California, 3 in New York, and 5 in Texas. This brings our total store count to 75 locations. Great job to everyone involved in the expansion efforts!", "create_at": 1696560000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "Hi Jason, thanks for sharing the Q3 new store openings report. Can you provide more details on the Texas locations? Which cities did we expand to?", "create_at": 1696561000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "retail-expansion", "channel": "new-store-openings", "user": "jlee", "message": "We opened 2 locations in Houston, 2 in Dallas, and 1 in Austin. All of these locations are now fully operational and receiving great customer feedback. I'll send over the detailed report to you via email.", "create_at": 1696562000000}}
